SYNTAX
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
inline   EXAMPLE:

<p style="color: red", "font size: 20px"; > HI </p>

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

internal 

inside <head> tag


<head>
<style>

 p {
   color: red;
   font size: 20px;
   } 

</head>

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
external 

<link href = "css/  style.css" type ="text/css" re="stylesheet" >

p {
   color: red;
   font size: 20px;
   } 
